Hati-hati, Mara.

00:56:59.851 --> 00:57:01.505
Terima kasih.

00:57:04.072 --> 00:57:05.726
As-salam alaykom.

00:57:07.206 --> 00:57:09.774
Wa Alykom As-slam.

